ValaTerm is a lightweight terminal written in Vala.

Build Requirements
==================

 * valac >= 0.12.1
 * gcc or Clang/LLVM
 * intltool
 * gettext
 * pkg-config

Run Requirements
================

 * glib-2.0 >= 2.6
 * gtk+-3.0 or gtk+-2.0 >= 2.16
 * vte-2.90 or vte >= 0.28

